[9111] = {'Robe of Faith', '<Father Montoy makes some strange gestures in the air in front of you.> Blessed <boy/girl>, have you found the vestments of the fallen? The poor souls whose last breaths were taken on the field of battle - stripped of everything including their dignity. Bring me the desecrated remnants of the departed along with reagents of purification and you shall know faith.', 'Father Inigo Montoy at Light\'s Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands will make a Robe of Faith if you bring him the following: 1 Desecrated Robe, 25 Wartorn Cloth Scraps, 4 Mooncloth and 2 Nexus Crystals.'},
